## DataService (`data_service.dart`)

### Purpose
Provides mock data for development and manages data operations.

### Responsibilities
- Generate sample data
- Simulate API responses
- Filter and search operations
- Data validation

### Pattern
```dart
class DataService {
  // Singleton
  static final DataService _instance = DataService._internal();
  factory DataService() => _instance;
  DataService._internal();
  
  // Mock data generators
  List<WikiArticle> getWikiArticles({String? category}) {
    final articles = _generateWikiArticles();
    if (category == null || category == 'all') return articles;
    return articles.where((a) => a.category == category).toList();
  }
  
  List<Post> getFeedPosts({String? category, int limit = 20}) {
    final posts = _generatePosts();
    if (category == null || category == 'featured') {
      return posts.take(limit).toList();
    }
    return posts
        .where((p) => p.category == category)
        .take(limit)
        .toList();
  }
  
  User? getUserById(String id) {
    return _generateUsers().firstWhere(
      (u) => u.id == id,
      orElse: () => _generateUsers().first,
    );
  }
  
  CampPlan? getActivePlan() {
    // Return from storage or mock
    return _generateSamplePlan();
  }
  
  // Private generators
  List<WikiArticle> _generateWikiArticles() {
    return [
      WikiArticle(
        id: '1',
        title: 'Tunnel Tent Setup 101',
        category: 'setup',
        difficulty: 'beginner',
        description: 'Stop struggling. Elegant setup techniques for solo campers.',
        // ... more fields
      ),
      // ... more articles
    ];
  }
  
  List<Post> _generatePosts() { /* ... */ }
  List<User> _generateUsers() { /* ... */ }
  CampPlan _generateSamplePlan() { /* ... */ }
}
```

### Data Generation Guidelines
- Use realistic data (real camping brands, locations)
- Include variety (different categories, difficulties)
- Make data relationships consistent (creator IDs match)
- Use placeholder URLs for images
- Add enough data for scrolling/testing

