## Future Extensions

When adding real APIs:
1. Create separate API service classes
2. Use repository pattern for data layer
3. Add caching strategies
4. Implement retry logic
5. Handle authentication tokens
6. Add offline support

Example structure:
```dart
// api_service.dart - HTTP client wrapper
// user_repository.dart - User data operations
// plan_repository.dart - Plan data operations
// cache_service.dart - Caching layer
```
